#X text 286 346 Design based on an analysis of the TB-303 by Robin
Whittle;
#X text 284 135 As I don't have a 303 at home \, I used Propellerheads
Rebirth RB-338 to match (or rather guesstimate) settings by ear.;
#X text 284 171 MIDI notes with a velocity of 100 or more are accentuated.
;
#X text 283 192 Vanilla friendly with a few additions:;
#X text 287 207 - settable pulse width for the rectangular waveform
\,;
#X text 287 246 - accent effect is split for VCF and VCA \,;
#X text 287 260 - filter saturation and oversampling provided by bob~.
;
